text: John Elias Baldacci (born January 30, 1955) is an American politician. He was the 73rd Governor of Maine from 2003 to 2011. He was a Democrat, he also was a member of the United States House of Representatives from 1995 to 2003.New York Times interview with John Baldacci, November 1, 2009. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Maine Category:United States representatives from Maine Category:Politicians from Bangor, Maine Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
